Title: Of Vampire Mirrors and Privacy Lamps: Privacy Management in Multi-User Augmented Environments  
Author: Andreas Butz, Clifford Beshers, Steven Feiner, 
Keyword: Augmented Reality, Virtual Reality, Privacy, Collaborative Work  
Address: San Francisco, CA,  1214 Amsterdam Ave.  New York, NY 10027,  
Affiliation: Technology),  Dept. of Computer Science,  CS Building, Columbia University,  
